data.description: Attention J O N E S County! FOUND your new home just a few minutes from downtown Macon!  Located just off of the Fall Line Freeway, this home is the perfect location for the Macon college student, or nurse!  This home has been well cared for and is ready for its new owners to move right in and make it theirs in 2024! It has three bedrooms, two and a half baths and a favorite feature of many is the loft area, perfect for a TV room, homework area for the kids or a nice reading nook. The owners fenced the backyard in completely and added a small storage building that is included in the sell. Come to Jones County today and let's make this home YOUR HOME!
